title: Preview: Season 19, Japanese Fairy Tales
description: Elizabeth previews Season 19, a selection of stories published between 1903 and 1908, from the book Japanese Fairy Tales by Yei Theodora Ozaki. To enjoy these episodes ad-free, try The Sleepy Bookshelf Premium free for 7 days: https://sleepybookshelf.supercast.com/.
